# A list of global css classes

icons: https://flushmodules.com/css/visuals/fm-icons.png

- ic-menu
- ic-flushmodules-a
- ic-flushmodules-b
- ic-notify
- ic-arrowdown
- ic-arrowup
- ic-arrowleft
- ic-arrowright
- ic-touch
- ic-mouse
- ic-search
- ic-pen
- ic-folder
- ic-gear-a
- ic-gear-b
- ic-chat
- ic-paint
- ic-photo
- ic-video
- ic-attachment
- ic-file-s
- ic-file

patterns: (repeated background)

- pt-trans (https://flushmodules.com/css/visuals/pattern-trans.gif)

overlays:

- ov-trigger (makes the element absoulte, transparent and fully covering the parent(needs position:relative;))
- ov-submit (submit button style)
- ov-button (button style)
- ov-arrow-up (arrow style)
- ov-arrow-down (..)
- ov-arrow-left (..)
- ov-arrow-right (..)
- ov-input (default style for input elements(data-valid="true/false" style for correct/false input))
- ov-fileinput (hides the default file input and makes it absolute and fully covering the parent(needs position:relative;))
- ov-pre (similar to html <pre> element style)
- ov-loading-s1 (default loading icon as background with min height/width)
- ov-loading-s2 (..)
- ov-ellipsis (nowrap, text ellipsis, no overflow)
- ov-centerer (used for centering inline-block elements vertically)
- ov-clear (clear float)
- ov-link (default link style)
- ov-playvideo (used for video play buttons on video preview images)

other:

- hide (hide element)
- hr (hr style)
